    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Invertebrate animals that are characterized by coelom or body cavity, or setae or movable bristles, and a body divided into segments by transverse rings or annulations.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
